<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans von Rosenberg</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, wegen der von Balthasar von Murach geplanten Überfälle nichts ausrichten zu können.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_128" id="63v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_128_r3l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hanſen <expan>vo<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Roſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_128_r3l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> her hans / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / vvie Jr gewarnt ſeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_128_r3l3">von cʒugriffe <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> die VValthaſar <expan>Mürach<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒetün main / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_128_r3l4">vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / . vnd wer vns das nicht lıeb ob es </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_128_r3l5">geſcheh / . Auch wiſſen wir von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> nichts dar cʒü cʒetün </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_128_r3l6">wan wir nichts wiſſen / daʒ er mit vns cʒeſchıcken hab / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_128_r3l7">hoffen / daʒ er ſich gen den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nicht vergreiffe / . wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_128_r3l8">erberkeit lıeb vnd <expan>frewntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir allcʒıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_128_r3l9"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> Sabato <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Eraſmj / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_128" id="63v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen <expan>vo<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her Hans, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, wie ir gewarnt
                        seit von czugriffe <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, die Walthasar
                                <expan>Mürach<ex>er</ex></expan> cze tün main,
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und wer uns das nicht
                        lieb, ob es gescheh. Auch wissen wir von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> nichts dar czü czetün, wan wir nichts wissen,
                        daz er mit uns cze schicken hab, und hoffen, daz er sich gen den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nicht vergreiffe. Wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit lieb und
                                <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        allczit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> sabato
                                <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Erasmi.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
